room_title: Escape room "Welcome to the Afterverse" by Totem Escape in San Jose
room_address: 19 N 2nd St Suite 206, San Jose, CA 95113
room_description: Race against time as you enter the dimension known as The Afterverse in search of The Necronomicon, an ancient text of unimaginable power, while a Cabal of Death Wizards closes in on you. You have one hour to accomplish your mission and get out or be lost in the Afterverse forever.
